 all graduate-level summer courses, please check the full schedule . See what we have offered in the past by checking out our course enrollment history .   4-Week Session Courses: MAY 18 – JUNE 12, 2020  8-Week Session Courses: JUNE 15 – AUGUST 7, 2020   Note: The course list is optimized to be viewed on a computer.  This page uses Javascript to deliver rich and dynamic content. For a full interactive experience please enable javascript in your browser. If you need further assistance please consult http://www.enable-javascript.com/ Select the session that you're interested in from the following lists: 4-week session 8-week session Δ This symbol means that the course is offered online.          Have a question? Chat live with Summer Session Staff!      Help desk software                UIC in the summer                        Links Contact Us  Sign up for E-mail Reminders  UIC Extended Campus  UIC Home  Disability Resources  Privacy Policy  Emergency Information    Loading      Have a question?  Give us a call, we can help! 312-996-9099     2016 University of Illinois at Chicago           php
